This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with automated translation lexicon induction and language annotation. It could also belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning) as these fields are closely related to natural language processing and language understanding. Additionally, it could be categorized under cs.IR (Information Retrieval) as it involves the extraction of etymological information from text. Finally, it could also be classified under cs.DL (Deep Learning) as deep learning techniques are often used in natural language processing tasks.
